Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.81,0:00:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and pick out some bread and drinks for breakfast tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't listen to a word people say...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... What do we need for a cold? Water, sports drinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dairy products and the like...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe some food that's easy on the stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we buy something for you to have for breakfast, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.05,0:00:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Cereal or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she catch it from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There are cold germs floating around all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes people catch it, and sometimes they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.03,0:00:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point worrying about who caught what from whom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I pick something to take with us when we go to see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Put it in the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Kouki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.81,0:01:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing in the sweets aisle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.73,0:01:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki! I told you to get something for breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.76,0:03:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We probably shouldn't go in, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll just be an extra worry for your mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The food's in here, so you can give it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum! Daikichi brought us food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to what people say, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kouki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. You've done so much for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I should be thanking you after all you did for Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She's much better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She went back to school today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening. It's good that you're all better, Rin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cooking up some of that rice porridge right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so I'll be better in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin! Let's go throw my tooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Kouki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nitani-san, you might have caught\Nthis because you watched over Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.75,Alt,,0,0,0,,We'll throw it from here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I come into contact with countless people each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.79,Alt,,0,0,0,,We're so high up...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.71,Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm going to throw it onto that roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Every day I ride a packed train to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.80,0:04:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee it came from her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least let me help with Kouki,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,even if it's just picking him up and bringing him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, we're going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, let's play video games!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, next time I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki... Make sure and help your mum, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.43,0:05:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The pudding and the smaller drink are from Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Rin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pudding is my favourite!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you up so early? It's Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.96,0:06:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you! We're practising for the skipping competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's wobbly, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Brush slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop wiggling it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be pushing yourself so hard yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for always taking advantage of your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think {\i1}I'm{\i0} the one who should be saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised Kouki's having such trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He just can't seem to get it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.47,0:06:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouki, you're jumping too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:07:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The jump rope whirls around like this, so you should be jumping here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So why are you moving your legs and arms at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Your move your arms first, and then your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,First, try it slowly once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.40,0:07:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! Me, too! Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your problem is that you're swinging\Nyour arms in circles that are too big, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your arms in like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're early!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see why they're so fired up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-kun's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because he has a big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He has someone to learn everything from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to join in, Sayaka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She just lost one of her upper teeth, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard being a girl, huh? Even as a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-chan... What sort of container do you hold your teeth in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your parents get you a cute one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know? There are cases that you can\Nput your kid's old baby teeth in as a memento.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A memento?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They have these tiny cute ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.72,Alt,,0,0,0,,Tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.76,Alt,,0,0,0,,Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Mine's a butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:20.18,Alt,,0,0,0,,I bought one for Kouki, too, but he doesn't save his teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin would love one of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm an idiot! I should've known there'd be something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I've met Rin, every day's been like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,freaking out and fussing over the tiniest things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, this is for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I drew it in school!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to write about a member of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You put your baby teeth in it when they fall out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,As a little keepsake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A keepsake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Kouki-kun's mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't that Kouki's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I throw mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've thrown all of mine on the roof until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.15,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can throw them or keep them. It's up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.17,0:09:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin. I'm going to give skipping my all next time, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're poking at your tooth again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave it alone, it'll come out on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, either way, she's going to look like someone punched her lights out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She won't be able to smile, at the very least...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you grown taller again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're going to do it, too, Daikichi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to pick up a little excess weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's tough when you get older, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to nip it in the bud, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi-san's doing it like a boxer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is easier on your knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi! Teach me how to do that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair! How come only you get to look cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to learn to do it normally first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, too! Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan! You can do it backwards! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.87,0:10:53.34,Alt,,0,0,0,,Kids sure are amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.75,0:10:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They have so much energy, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock! Paper! Scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.51,Alt,,0,0,0,,I don't know where they get it from.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.06,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Though, adults are pretty amazing, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.60,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you already know, but I'm not Rin's dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We only started living together a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, I spent all of my time just thinking about myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but once I met her, my whole lifestyle changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys have been with your kids their whole lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still pretty new to this, so it's not really a big deal yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm wondering if it's really possible to deal with...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...never having any real alone time again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.98,0:11:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rin... Wasn't today the skipping competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.04,0:12:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How many skips did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terri{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What about backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Two hundred and three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do that many?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that got you... first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the certificate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure did well! This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But I could've done way better on forward jumping...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you did only get one chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.53,0:12:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're really good at it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that, even if they don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we almost there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... About ten more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll want to see that wobbly tooth of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you not to touch it unless you need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll show them my skipping, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown so much recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Mum and Dad are going to get a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I'm taller than Auntie now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you've grown {\i1}that{\i0} much...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to go and fill Granddad in on things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rin-chan! I've been waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:14:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you one of the the biggest in your class?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have called! I would have come to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin is capable of walking for ten minutes, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be taller than me soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Kazumi-oneechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo. You're here early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I arrived a while before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.88,0:14:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Those clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They were yours, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie sent them to me a while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan, let me see your teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of the front teeth are wobbly just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay? It doesn't hurt, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts a little sometimes, but I'm used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.82,0:14:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you do anything to help her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Her gums are all red!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a little swelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, when I was younger, you said you'd pull mine out with thread!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.29,Alt,,0,0,0,,With thread?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.29,0:15:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My! I don't quite remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to make everything easy to chew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some freeze-dried tofu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have some beans, too, Auntie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You just eat up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I love freeze-dried tofu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.70,0:15:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it fall out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.29,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood! Blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum! A tissue! A tissue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin, use this for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a dust cloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan has changed so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's always been like that on the inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're getting married, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum told me earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice. She said that he seemed like a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The only problem is that he wants kids straight away...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.33,0:16:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No going out drinking. No concerts.\NNo holidays. No good food.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.38,0:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to do anything anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should be talking to him about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's not much I can say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not even into kids to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't want to become one of those obnoxious mums!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I could sacrifice myself just to raise a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, I think you'd make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If you really wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess when the kid's already there, you don't really have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's easy for you to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it's like to be a husband. Nor a father. Nor a mother, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I might not have time to go shopping or sit around drinking tea,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but my time at work is my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And my time with my son is my own, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it is precious to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's any special trick to being a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck, the world's full of people just like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.81,0:18:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Granddad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My adult teeth are starting to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, "Cheese!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.32,0:19:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That vase...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Masako-san had one just like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! The other one feels like it's going to come out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirror! Mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that I'll go on fussing and worrying over the smallest things...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Though that's probably true of all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.03,0:20:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck? You look like a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Send a text to your parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.05,Alt,,0,0,0,,A photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever else happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'll go on being happy when I see her smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Open your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think things are just fine like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Daikichi!
